{"product_id":"madara-sos-sensitive-moisturiser","title":"MÁDARA SOS+ Sensitive Moisturiser 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis lightweight moisturiser improves the hydration of sensitive, easily irritated, redness-prone skin. Biotechnologically obtained molecules of seaweed work to balance the skin's microbiome and reinforce its natural protection against external stressors. Minimises the appearance of redness and burning.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply to clean skin daily. Use in combination with MÁDARA SOS+ Sensitive Night Cream for the best results.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe) Leaf Juice, Glycerin, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Pentylene Glycol, Polyglyceryl-3 Stearate, Cetearyl Alcohol, Sodium PCA, Coco- Caprylate, Isoamyl Laurate, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Aqua, Hydrolyzed Rhodophyceae Extract, Octyldodecanol, Xanthan Gum, Cellulose, Irvingia gabonensis kernel butter, Potassium Hydroxide, Sodium Hyaluronate, Hydrogenated Coco-glycerides, Tocopherol, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Sodium phytate, Hydrolyzed Hyaluronic Acid\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e* Please note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49858966782279,"sku":"","price":39.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-sos-sensitive-moisturiser-50ml-643317.jpg?v=1739897262","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/madara-sos-sensitive-moisturiser","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}